const defaultAreEqual = (args, pArgs) =>
  args[0] === pArgs[0] &&
  args[1] === pArgs[1] &&
  args[2] === pArgs[2] &&
  args[3] === pArgs[3]

const memoOne = (fn, areEqual) => {
  const equal = areEqual || defaultAreEqual
  let args = [],
    value
  return function () {
    if (equal(arguments, args)) return value
    args = arguments
    value = fn.apply(this, args)
    return value
  }
}

export default memoOne
